{"tid":39672,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇Grand Tour] AmazonPrime Video登陸香港, 收費USD2.99 6個月","createTime":"2016-12-14T17:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T11:13:18.000Z","uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6dd6fcd4642183852e9eeceaa1e4a838aa6c63","tid":39672,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g2f4wavm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg2f4wavm&h=9a487e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAmazon Prime Video: <a href=\"http://primevideo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprimevideo.com&d=YXKoEk3gQ%2FwtUo%2BI4pDMi3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=78329a25\" target=\"_blank\">primevideo.com</a><br />\n<br />\nAmazon Prime Video平過Netflix勁多　　正式殺入香港睇The Grand Tour<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當Top Gear後代的節目The Grand Tour登場時，Amazon已經暗示會在十二月在全球登錄。日前，他們宣佈正式在超過200個國家登錄，中國大陸並不包括在內，但香港則有份。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon Prime Video香港都會有The Grand Tour，而且月費亦較Netflix便宜得多。目前在推廣期間，首六個月月費為US$2.99，其後月費為US$5.99，可以有七天試用，仍然比Netflix便宜，有興趣可到專有網站PrimeVideo申請，app同樣可以讓用家下載節目離線收看。除了The Grand Tour外，Amazon Prime Video也有不少電影和原創電視節目，包括The Man in the High Castle、Transparent、Mozart in the Jungle等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2016/12/amazon-prime-video-hongkong-the-grand-tour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2016%2F12%2Famazon-prime-video-hongkong-the-grand-tour%2F&d=YXKoEk3gQ%2FwtUo%2BI4pDMi3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3cf62460\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2016/12/amazon-prime-video-hongkong-the-grand-tour/</a><br />\n<br />\n即刻試用唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f16f50fb994c45c092ab68a28c1741b7e4f60e7","tid":39672,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1657b88539d3da257af4